絞肉的主要成份是骨骼肌；由於消費者的偏好和需求，市面上販售的絞肉常提供各種不同的脂肪比例，通常在脂肪比例在5~30%之間。美國的牛絞肉依法不得超過30%脂肪。<ref name=factsheet />

研究發現絞肉的成分包括[[結締組織|結締組織]]、[[周圍神經|周圍神經]]、[[血管|血管]]、[[脂肪組織|脂肪組織]]等等。有些樣本中有植物、[[骨頭|骨頭]]、或[[軟骨|軟骨]]。水含量佔40~60%。<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.hnossalmeron.com/hamburguesas/prayson_anndiagpath_dec2008.pdf|title=Fast food hamburgers: what are we really eating?|journal=Annals of Diagnostic Pathology|volume=12|year=2008|page=406–409|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131210120155/http://www.hnossalmeron.com/hamburguesas/prayson_anndiagpath_dec2008.pdf|archivedate=2013-12-10}}</ref>

==安全==
完整的肉在內部通常是[[無菌|無菌]]的，相較之下，絞肉在切碎的過程中，表面積大增，[[微生物|微生物]]被打散到各處，所以被汙染的風險大增，通常必須全熟才能食用<ref>Committee on the Review of the USDA E. coli O157:H7, "Farm-to-Table Process Risk Assessment", Slaughter Module in ''Escherichia coli O157:H7 in Ground Beef: Review of a Draft Risk Assessment'', 2002, The National Academies Press, Washington, DC.</ref><ref>Honikel, K. O., "Minced Meats", in ''Encyclopedia of Meat Sciences'', Jensen, W. K., et al., eds., 2004, Elsevier, New York.</ref>。未熟的[[漢堡肉|漢堡肉]]曾造成上百人食物中毒<ref>[http://www.ou.edu/deptcomm/dodjcc/groups/02C2/Jack%20in%20the%20Box.htm Case Study]: Jack in the Box ''E. coli'' crisis</ref>。

